SUMMARY:BackstageCon Hosted by CNCF - Full-Day Event | ALL ACCESS PASS REQUIRED
DESCRIPTION:BackstageCon schedule is now LIVE!\n\nBackstageCon is a one-day conference focused on all things Backstage: an open framework for building developer portals. At BackstageCon\, we’ll provide a vendor-neutral space for collaboration and learning centered on improving developer experience and effectiveness through open source technologies.The event is vendor-neutral and organized by members of the Backstage community. To learn more please visit the event's&nbsp\;website.For questions regarding this event\, please reach out to&nbsp\;cncfcolocatedevents@linuxfoundation.org.
