DTSTART:20260323T124700Z
DTEND:20260323T125200Z
SUMMARY:Project Lightning Talk: Envoy Today: What’s New In Managing Cloud-Native And AI Workload Traffic? - Karol Szwaj\, Maintainer
DESCRIPTION:Learn about improvements that make Envoy faster\, easier to operate\, and more adaptable—especially for teams building modern cloud-native and AI-driven systems\, which impose a set of new requirements on the networking traffic management.\n\nWe will share highlights from the Envoy project ecosystem\, new features from recent releases and important news from the whole community.\n\nLastly\, we’ll touch on where the project is headed and how these changes reinforce Envoy’s role as a reliable\, flexible data plane for the next generation of applications\, together with Envoy AI Gateway and Envoy Gateway.
CATEGORIES:PROJECT OPPORTUNITIES
LOCATION:Elicium 2\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
