SUMMARY:Project Lightning Talk: What's New And Exciting In Kagent? - Peter Jausovec\, Maintainer
DESCRIPTION:Kagent brings agentic AI to cloud native. It's a tool for DevOps and platform engineers to build\, deploy\, and run AI-powered solutions in Kubernetes.\n\nThis talk will provide a summary of the progress made in kagent over the past year\, as well as an overview of the roadmap and future plans.
CATEGORIES:PROJECT OPPORTUNITIES
LOCATION:Elicium 2\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:f7a875977a036797cbf7e7ad00060254
URL:http://kccnceu2026.sched.com/event/f7a875977a036797cbf7e7ad00060254
