DTSTART:20260323T144500Z
DTEND:20260323T145000Z
SUMMARY:Project Lightning Talk: Perses General Overview - Augustin Husson\, Maintainer
DESCRIPTION:This session will give a general overview of Perses and short update about what is happening in the project.
CATEGORIES:PROJECT OPPORTUNITIES
LOCATION:Elicium 2\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:244e0266896df876b45f1d52eeff4cb2
