SUMMARY:Keynote: Welcome + Opening Remarks - Jonathan Bryce\, Executive Director\, Cloud and Infrastructure\, Linux Foundation & Chris Aniszczyk\, CTO\, Cloud and Infrastructure\, Linux Foundation
DESCRIPTION:\n
CATEGORIES:KEYNOTE SESSIONS
LOCATION:Hall 12\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:6d33234981cf5b14145b63b75fa9e0c0
