SUMMARY:Network Nook Meetup: 1st Time Attendees
DESCRIPTION:Join us for casual and engaging meetups at the Network Nook during lunch breaks! These informal gatherings are open to all\, whether you're a first-time attendee\, a solo traveler\, or simply looking to chat about shared interests. This is a great way to connect with others.\n\nToday's topic: 1st Time Attendees\nNew to KubeCon + CloudNativeCon? Connect with fellow first-time attendees\, share tips\, and get insights from CNCF ambassadors on how to make the most of your conference experience!
CATEGORIES:EXPERIENCES
