SUMMARY:Cloud Native Theater | Cloud Native University: From Control Planes to Cognitive Planes: Agentic Architecture with MCP - Eddie Wassef\, Archetypical Software
DESCRIPTION:APIs helped define cloud-native—but agentic systems need more.\n \n In this talk\, we introduce MCP (Model\, Context\, Protocol)—an architectural framework built for adaptive\, AI-enhanced\, agentic systems. You'll learn how MCP extends API-centric thinking to define not just interfaces\, but also capabilities\, environment-aware behavior\, and reflective discovery.
CATEGORIES:SOLUTIONS SHOWCASE
