DTSTAMP:20260303T114022Z
DTSTART:20260324T133000Z
DTEND:20260324T140000Z
SUMMARY:What's New in gRPC - Kevin Nilson & John Feig\, Google
DESCRIPTION:This talk will go through all the exciting new features we have recently added to gRPC. We will be covering topics such as OpenTelemetry\, Service Mesh\, K8s Gateway APIs and GAMMA. We will also cover tips and tricks for building a Microservices Application with gRPC.
CATEGORIES:MAINTAINER TRACK
LOCATION:E106-108\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:29b6653e7274652f4ae5d6e3d6b9ae31
URL:http://kccnceu2026.sched.com/event/29b6653e7274652f4ae5d6e3d6b9ae31
END:VEVENT
