SUMMARY:Sponsored Demo: Meet Klaudia: The Autonomous AI SRE Platform by Komodor
DESCRIPTION:The scale and complexity of modern cloud-native infrastructure are exceeding human capacity. Most practitioners have embraced the idea of AI SRE\, but are still cautious about enabling it to operate autonomously in production. In this session\, you will see why Klaudia stands out among emerging AI SREs as the most comprehensive\, mature\, and reliable solution - chosen by the world’s largest enterprises. Watch Klaudia automatically:\n - Detecting\, investigating\, and remediating even the most complex issues\n - Optimizing costs without impacting reliability\n - Adapting contextually to unique environments and use cases\n Learn how we built (and continuously validate) the multi-agentic architecture that delivers accurate results at scale and earns the trust of platform teams across industries.\n \n \n **In order to facilitate networking and business relationships at the event\, you may choose to visit a third party’s booth or access sponsored content. You are never required to visit third party booths or to access sponsored content. When visiting a booth or participating in sponsored activities\, the third party will receive some of your registration data. This data includes your first name\, last name\, title\, company\, address\, email\, standard demographics questions (i.e. job function\, industry)\, and details about the sponsored content or resources you interacted with. If you choose to interact with a booth or access sponsored content\, you are explicitly consenting to receipt and use of such data by the third-party recipients\, which will be subject to their own privacy policies.**
