DTEND:20260325T111500Z
SUMMARY:🚨 Contribfest: Headlamp: Build Kubernetes Experiences Your Way! - Joaquim Rocha & Santhosh Nagaraj\, Microsoft
DESCRIPTION:Join the Headlamp maintainers for a hands‑on workshop on how to extend Headlamp to include a UI for your favorite project\, Custom Resources\, or CNCF tool! Headlamp is an extensible Kubernetes UI that is officially part of the Kubernetes project (under the SIG UI). It offers a great base UX for managing Kubernetes\, and a comprehensive plugin system for creating new interfaces and experiences. In this session\, you will learn to build a Headlamp plugin\, with the assistance of Headlamp's maintainers. You will leave with knowledge of how Headlamp's plugins work\, and it's hopefully the kickstart of a new UI for your projects that you may choose to also publish with the community. If you are already experienced in Headlamp\, this Contribfest session is still a great chance to have discussions with maintainers and the community\, in order to take your contributions further. Do not forget to bring your laptop\, and we hope to see you!
CATEGORIES:🚨 CONTRIBFEST
LOCATION:G107\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
