SUMMARY:SIG-Windows Updates - Mark Rossetti\, Microsoft & JR Valdes\, Red Hat
DESCRIPTION:At this maintainer track talk we will cover what is new in the Windows Special Interest Group. This talk will focus on improvements to our test infrastructure\, and highlight some of the features we plan to GA in upcoming Kubernetes releases.
