SUMMARY:🚨 Contribfest: Prometheus New Contributor Introduction - Bryan Boreham\, Grafana Labs; Saswata Mukherjee\, Red Hat; Arianna Vespri\, OllyGarden; Ben Kochie\, Reddit
DESCRIPTION:Prometheus is an extremely popular Open Source monitoring system\, with over a million installations. The project relies entirely on volunteer contributions\, with no commercial owner or enterprise version. \n If you have recently made your first PR to Prometheus\, or you would like to know more about the process\, come along! We will walk through one contribution\, then open the floor for your questions. \n Suited to people who know how Go or React\, or are interested in other project aspects such as documentation.
CATEGORIES:🚨 CONTRIBFEST
LOCATION:G107\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
