DTSTAMP:20260303T114022Z
DTSTART:20260326T080000Z
DTEND:20260326T080500Z
SUMMARY:Keynote: Welcome Back + Opening Remarks
DESCRIPTION:
CATEGORIES:KEYNOTE SESSIONS
LOCATION:Hall 12\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:49219e62f1864ed8e07558e50c46dee7
URL:http://kccnceu2026.sched.com/event/49219e62f1864ed8e07558e50c46dee7
