SUMMARY:Learning Lounge: CNPA or CNPE? Roles\, Skills & Which One is Right For You? - Alex Coma\, Linux Foundation Education
DESCRIPTION:10-Minute Tip Talk
CATEGORIES:SOLUTIONS SHOWCASE
