DTSTAMP:20260303T114022Z
DTSTART:20260326T124500Z
DTEND:20260326T131500Z
SUMMARY:BoF: AI Infrastructure and Platform: LLMs\, Agentic AI
DESCRIPTION:Cloud native is an excellent choice to running AI worklaods&nbsp\;\n\nTopics to be included but open to other topics during the session.\nBest practices for generic MLOps on cloud native platforms\, including tools such as kubeflow and mlflow as well as specific tools for LLMs and Agentic AIMost common pain points of running such workloads on cloud native infraGaps in the existing ecosystem\n
CATEGORIES:EXPERIENCES
