DTSTAMP:20260303T114022Z
DTSTART:20260326T133000Z
DTEND:20260326T140000Z
SUMMARY:BoF: Infrastructure Optimization for GPUs / Inference / Training / Networking
DESCRIPTION:Advanced capabilities required for AI and ML workloads on cloud native infrastructure are not necessarily available by default\, requiring effort to optimize the infrastructure and scheduling.\n\nTopics to be included but open to other topics during the session.\nLow level runtime optimizations\, including CPU/GPU NUMA affinity\, CPU pinning and other required configurationsLow latency networking support for Infiniband and RDMA over Converged Ethernet (RoCEv2)\, required for multi node training and inferenceSupport for heterogeneous hardware\, multiple GPU vendors\, integration of FPGAs and other specialized accelerators\n
CATEGORIES:EXPERIENCES
